      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the reassurance. i was worried it might be an infection but you make it sound like it's just part of the process. do you think i should use any specific ointment? like should i use a lot of it to make sure it stays sterile, or just a thin layer? also can i put a bandaid over it after the compress to keep it covered? i dont want to bother the surgeon if it's just normal healing.",
